 為左用少D錢, 唔怕老實講, 底褲都要著完前面反轉再著多一日, 點解咁做呢? 因為可以洗少一次, 用少一次水, 真係想用少D錢, 對抗通脹!<br />\n<br />\n但竟然, 放左工都要見到呢張 poster ?! Inflation Leung, 放過我啦!!!"},{"pid":"347d678582e7181a7a5c46089a030645563d0fa6","tid":507531,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"樓上做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5beb055021298893ce13b47e753bb62430e580ed","tid":507531,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"347d678582e7181a7a5c46089a030645563d0fa6","tid":507531,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"樓上做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"潮文嚟"}]}